{pageend:Throw the Berry into the pot and get stirring!}
Watch for an arrow to show you which direction
{pageend:to stir.}
Be quick! If you stir too slowly, you’ll burn the
batter. But not too quick! If you stir too fast,
{pageend:the batter will overflow.}
{pageend:If you do well, you’ll cook up a delicious Poffin!}
By the way, you can also make Poffins at
Amity Square!

